  "description": "Five layers, fold point at 0.35, high fold amount, symmetry at 0.45. The slightly asymmetric fold at a sub-midpoint position creates tessellating harmonic patterns — each layer adds a reflection of the previous layer's fold structure. A lead voice that sounds like a geometric tiling of a single waveform.",
